                    <span>I really liked this book as a Beginner since it teaches a lot about the visual studio environment and also takes you step-by-step through applications. Not the greatest in-depth or and by no means advanced. But its super for a beginner.If you know little of VC++ and even less of MFC then START here. Notice I emphasized Start....since you will need to read lots of other books to gain deeper understanding. Take this from someone who struggled with the advanced books and then got a better start with this one.</span>
                  
